<p>定義 Date</p>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>Date =OFFSET($A$2,0,0,COUNTA($A:$A)-1)
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>(A欄 第 2列 個開始)</p>

<p>定義 MAX</p>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>Max =OFFSET($B$2,0,0,COUNTA($B:$B)-1)
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>(B欄 第 2列 個開始)</p>

<p>定義 AVE</p>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>AVE =OFFSET($C$2,0,0,COUNTA($C:$C)-1)
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>圖表內</p>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>=SERIES("Max",Book1!Date,Book1!Max,1)
=SERIES("AVE",Book1!Date,Book1!AVE,2)
=SERIES("名稱"，X軸，數值，第幾個項目)
=SERIES("最大值",'月值統計表.xlsx'!Date,'月值統計表.xlsx'!MAX,1)
</code></pre></div></div>
